unittitle_ssm: Service Employees International Union, Local 32BJ Photographs and Archived Websites
abstract_ssm: This collection contains photographs and websites of the Service Employees International Union, Local 32BJ. The collection contains mostly black and white photographs from the late 1930s and 1940s of strikes and group portraits of union leaders.
